import { memo } from 'react' import { english, vietnamese } from '../../Languages/InformationCustomerRegisterTourPrivate' function InformationCustomerRegisterTourPrivate({ languageSelected, customerRegisted, setCustomerRegisted }) { const languageList = languageSelected === 'EN' ? english : vietnamese return (
setPhone(e.target.value)} placeholder={languageList.txtEnterPhone} className="input-inline" />
setEmail(e.target.value)} placeholder={languageList.txtEnterEmail} className='input-inline' />
) } export default memo(InformationCustomerRegisterTourPrivate)
